tasks.title: Project 8
tasks.description:
User Story — Leave Request Validation & Decision

As a Leave Manager Agent
I want to evaluate an employee’s leave request using standard thinking steps
So that I can return an accurate approval or rejection decision.

Standard Thinking Steps Used
Step Type	Description	Example in the Story
Collect Inputs	Gather request details	Employee ID, leave type, start/end dates
Retrieve Data	Fetch HR records	Get employee balance, attendance history
Check Policy	Validate rules	Policy for minimum balance, blackout dates
Calculate	Compute needed values	Calculate requested leave days
Call API	Confirm external data	Query Holiday API for official holidays
Generate Response	Return structured result	Decision + reason + updated balance
Thinking Outline Example

Collect Inputs: Employee ID E123, leave type Annual, start 2025-11-28, end 2025-12-02.

Retrieve Data:
• Current annual leave balance: 7 days
• Leave history: No penalty flags
• HR contract type: Full-time

Check Policy:
• Must have balance >= requested days
• Maximum 5 consecutive working days allowed
• Not allowed during blackout period for department X (checked = allowed)

Calculate:
Requested working days = 3 (weekend excluded)
New balance if approved = 7 - 3 = 4 days

Call API:
Holiday API → Verify there are 0 public holidays during requested dates

Generate Response:
Approve (balance sufficient + policy compliant)
Updated balance = 4 days
